00:26:15.774 --> 00:26:18.210 align:middle line:84%
>> Witches, it's a
fascinating field.

00:26:18.210 --> 00:26:19.411 align:middle line:84%
>> Leanne Marrama: It
is a fascinating field.

00:26:19.411 --> 00:26:21.279 align:middle line:84%
>> What about children who
want to dabble in this?

00:26:21.279 --> 00:26:23.181 align:middle line:90%
