wanted to study witchcraft.

00:26:36.928 --> 00:26:38.463 align:middle line:84%
>> Leanne Marrama:
It's just a religion.

00:26:38.463 --> 00:26:39.231 align:middle line:90%
It's believing in -

00:26:39.231 --> 00:26:40.065 align:middle line:90%
>> -- but don't you agree?

