00:26:41.466 --> 00:26:43.468 align:middle line:84%
>> Leanne Marrama: Some do, some
do freak, but most of, I think -

00:26:43.468 --> 00:26:46.204 align:middle line:84%
>> -- you don't seem to
be a bad person at all.

00:26:46.204 --> 00:26:47.272 align:middle line:90%
>> Leanne Marrama: No.

00:26:47.272 --> 00:26:48.573 align:middle line:84%
>> -- you actually
would probably be fun.

00:26:48.573 --> 00:26:51.543 align:middle line:84%
>> Leanne Marrama: I go to
church, I sit in the woods,

00:26:51.543 --> 00:26:56.181 align:middle line:84%
