00:26:56.181 --> 00:26:58.784 align:middle line:84%
to help and who we're going to
heal and what we need to get rid

00:26:58.784 --> 00:27:02.421 align:middle line:84%
of in our lives and we
connect with the seasons.

00:27:02.421 --> 00:27:04.189 align:middle line:90%
All of that is great for kids.

00:27:04.189 --> 00:27:07.192 align:middle line:84%
Paganism and witchcraft is
not a bad path for kids.

00:27:07.192 --> 00:27:09.060 align:middle line:90%
There's no words of the devil.

00:27:09.060 --> 00:27:11.997 align:middle line:84%
We don't hurt animals,
we honor animals.

00:27:11.997 --> 00:27:13.365 align:middle line:90%
It's actually safe.

00:27:13.365 --> 00:27:15.233 align:middle line:84%
So that, you know,
whether or not you're going

00:27:15.233 --> 00:27:19.004 align:middle line:84%
to raise your child within
the craft and if you're going

00:27:19.004 --> 00:27:21.807 align:middle line:84%
to raise your kid to
be a wiccan or however,

00:27:21.807 --> 00:27:24.976 align:middle line:84%
that's just like raising
your kids in any other faith,

00:27:24.976 --> 00:27:27.512 align:middle line:84%
