to say is completely different

00:27:50.335 --> 00:27:51.870 align:middle line:90%
on a level of faith, all right?

00:27:51.870 --> 00:27:53.071 align:middle line:90%
>> Are you one of them too?

00:27:53.071 --> 00:27:54.840 align:middle line:84%
>> Leanne Marrama: I am
