00:28:00.712 --> 00:28:01.913 align:middle line:90%
>> Anton LaVeyan.

00:28:01.913 --> 00:28:05.617 align:middle line:84%
>> Leanne Marrama: Anton
LaVeyan, they're actually,

00:28:05.617 --> 00:28:10.088 align:middle line:84%
