00:28:13.959 --> 00:28:18.129 align:middle line:84%
It would be un-Satanic
to hurt anybody

00:28:18.129 --> 00:28:22.067 align:middle line:84%
because it would not make
sense with their religion

00:28:22.067 --> 00:28:24.369 align:middle line:84%
