to put man above itself

00:28:24.369 --> 00:28:25.737 align:middle line:90%
and not disrespect other men.

00:28:25.737 --> 00:28:27.739 align:middle line:90%
>> But they worship the devil?

00:28:27.739 --> 00:28:29.941 align:middle line:84%
>> Leanne Marrama: Ah, LeVeyan
Satanists do not worship the

00:28:29.941 --> 00:28:32.410 align:middle line:84%
