00:28:33.612 --> 00:28:35.480 align:middle line:84%
>> -- then why do they
call themselves Satanists?

00:28:35.480 --> 00:28:36.815 align:middle line:84%
>> Leanne Marrama: Because
I think it's a tongue

00:28:36.815 --> 00:28:40.051 align:middle line:84%
in cheek thing because they're
on some essence the energy

00:28:40.051 --> 00:28:42.921 align:middle line:90%
