Satanists they love the animals,

00:28:53.565 --> 00:28:56.468 align:middle line:84%
they love their kids,
they love their lives,

00:28:56.468 --> 00:28:59.271 align:middle line:90%
they've never harmed anyone.

00:28:59.271 --> 00:29:03.174 align:middle line:84%
When you talk about Satan as
a living, breathing thing,

00:29:03.174 --> 00:29:07.012 align:middle line:84%
which is we, you know, witches
we don't believe in the devil.

00:29:07.012 --> 00:29:10.148 align:middle line:84%
